metadata.name: MoonChad 1
metadata.description: Meet the cosmic casanova created by artist DoopyDooDaa. He is a self taught artist whose style is inspired by graphic novels.Drawing characters has been a hobby for him for years now. MoonChad is a stoic hero that been displaced on a foreign planet.He uses his wits and charm to get out of the difficult positions he typically finds himself in. He doesnt always rely on just himself but looks to his crew mates to overcome seemingly impossible situations. This 70's comic book style character has over 160 characteristics distributed between 15 different traits. Reach for the stars with a MoonChad today! Website: nfturbo.io Discord: https://discord.gg/4PNAskg5QX Twitter: https://twitter.com/nfturboArt
